At this very moment, I don't think there is that much need to solve this 
problem. The technology to copy yourself is out of reach, isn't it? 
Before that, we're facing another problem: what about simulated 
consciousness. We kill most animals without really caring, but what about 
killing a simulation of a human identity - simply switching the power off 
