> On  Sat, 8 Nov 1997  Hal Finney <hal@rain.org> Wrote:
>         >No, Pw has been proven to have larger cardinality than aleph null,
>         >and it has been proven to have the same cardinality as the real
>         >numbers. But it is not known whether it is equal to aleph one. [...]
>         >Show me such a proof!
